=== ver17 test suite (verbose diagnostics) ===
TEST_VERBOSE=1  (set to 0 to reduce prints)

--- test_fresnel_rewrap_vs_pymoosh ---
[TEST] Fresnel (rewrap convention) interface r vs PyMoosh
  compares: rw._interface_r  <->  PyMoosh.coefficient_S on a single interface
  grid    : lam_nm=[450.0, 550.0, 650.0], u=[0.0, 0.5, 0.9], pol in {TE(0),TM(1)}
  criterion: atol=1e-10 OR rtol=1e-10

[CHECK] rewrap interface r vs PyMoosh (pol=0)
  context: n1=(1+0j), n2=(1.5+0j), u=0.0, lam_nm=[450.0, 550.0, 650.0]
  criterion: PASS if max|Δ|<= 1.000e-10 OR max_rel<= 1.000e-10
  result   : max|Δ|=8.327e-17, max_rel=8.327e-17 => PASS
  x   sample: [-0.2+0j, -0.2+0j, -0.2+0j]
  ref sample: [-0.2+0j, -0.2+0j, -0.2+0j]

[CHECK] rewrap interface r vs PyMoosh (pol=1)
  context: n1=(1+0j), n2=(1.5+0j), u=0.0, lam_nm=[450.0, 550.0, 650.0]
