--- test_gpvm_fresnel_sign_convention ---
[TEST] GPVM Fresnel sign convention
  TE: gpvm.fresnel_rt should match rewrap interface r
  TM: gpvm.fresnel_rt should equal - rewrap interface r (convention difference)
  note: set n_e=1 so u is identical in both conventions
  criterion: atol=1e-10 OR rtol=1e-10

[CHECK] GPVM TE Fresnel == rewrap
  context: nj=(1+0j), nk=(1.5+0j), u=0.0, lam_nm=[450.0, 550.0, 650.0]
  criterion: PASS if max|Δ|<= 1.000e-10 OR max_rel<= 1.000e-10
  result   : max|Δ|=8.327e-17, max_rel=8.327e-17 => PASS
  x   sample: [-0.2+0j, -0.2+0j, -0.2+0j]
  ref sample: [-0.2+0j, -0.2+0j, -0.2+0j]

[CHECK] GPVM TM Fresnel == -rewrap
